### Create Category Meta
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1/meta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Browse our wide selection of consumer electronics including phones, laptops, cameras and more.",
  "seo-title": "Electronics - Best Deals on Tech",
  "seo-description": "Shop the best electronics at unbeatable prices. Find smartphones, laptops, tablets and more."
}

###

### Create Meta - Only description (optional fields)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories/2/meta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Explore the latest fashion trends for men and women."
}

###

### Create Meta - SEO fields only
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories/3/meta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seo-title": "Home & Garden",
  "seo-description": "Discover everything for your home and garden."
}

###

### Create Meta - Category not found (expects 404)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories/9999/meta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "This should fail."
}

###

### Create Meta - SEO title too long (expects validation error)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories/4/meta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seo-title": "This title is intentionally way too long and should exceed the maximum allowed length for an SEO title field validation test case that will trigger a constraint violation"
}
